  "text": "A strict application of 'ghetto' to a number of different marginalised spaces, including Gypsy and Traveller sites, is problematic, as shown in the arguments within the evolving literature on this subject. Nonetheless, it is a useful frame for discussion to take debates forward, rather than continue in a circular argument of what exactly a ghetto is based on an American type model. Indeed [CITATION_1] points to this usefulness if we look to an evolution of the term, rather than strict application of ghetto criteria.",
